'''Grand Duke''' was a title of nobility on [[Eiattu 6]]. [[Gror Pernon]], a leading member of the [[Priamsta]], held the title as of [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]].

During the [[New Republic era]], Pernon encouraged his grand-niece, [[Isplourrdacartha Estillo|Plourr Ilo]] to return to [[Eiattu 6]] with the [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] to take back the throne from [[Harrandatha Estillo (impostor)|the impostor]] Prince [[Harrandatha Estillo|Harran]].

